data.description: Completely remodeled Lake township brick ranch.  Featuring 4 Beds, 2 full baths.  The house sits on a fenced 1 acre lot. The living room features a wood burning fireplace. Updated kitchen with custom cabinets and all appliances included.  A family room off the kitchen is perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the parklike backyard with above ground pool and firepit.  Updated bath just completed in 2023.  New Roof in 2020. Nothing to do but move in!
